## Locator Strategy (Priority Order)

Use this priority when choosing locators:

| Priority | Strategy | Example |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| 1st ✅ | Role-based (ARIA) | `page.getByRole(AriaRole.BUTTON, new Page.GetByRoleOptions().setName("Submit"))` |
| 2nd ✅ | Test ID | `page.getByTestId("login-btn")` |
| 3rd ✅ | Label | `page.getByLabel("Username")` |
| 4th ✅ | Placeholder | `page.getByPlaceholder("Enter email")` |
| 5th ⚠️ | CSS selector | `page.locator("#username")` |
| 6th ❌ | XPath | `page.locator("//input[@id='user']")` — avoid if possible |

