## Common Playwright Actions

```java
// Click
page.click("selector");

// Type / Fill
page.fill("selector", "text");

// Select dropdown
page.selectOption("select#country", "India");

// Checkbox
page.check("input[type='checkbox']");

// Wait for element
page.waitForSelector(".success-banner");

// Wait for URL
page.waitForURL("**/dashboard");

// Get text
String text = page.textContent(".heading");

// Is visible
boolean visible = page.isVisible(".modal");

// Screenshot
page.screenshot(new Page.ScreenshotOptions().setPath(Paths.get("screenshot.png")));

// Hover
page.hover(".menu-item");

// Keyboard
page.press("input", "Enter");
```

